{"tid":569191,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人對住其他人係另一個自己","createTime":"2018-02-22T12:55:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-22T13:45:46.000Z","uid":47052,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"cde4ca068a4446750fa020fdd7b905d0d4355423","tid":569191,"uid":47052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T12:55:34.000Z","msg":"係其他人眼中，我好樂觀開朗，面掛笑容，佢地以為呢個係真正既我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實真正既我悲觀又有抑鬱症，日日都諗緊點自殺....<br />\n我諗冇人會信我想自殺，真係自殺死咗佢地都未必信....<br />\n<br />\n個個以為我好多朋友，其實我冇乜朋友，放假都冇人約....<br />\n<br />\n我好驚俾人發現呢個真我，好驚佢地會嫌棄我，冇人會鍾意同一個負能量散播者玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b69a5d04f9eb7d956e6f0d1bf2c82d2f5a7b561","tid":569191,"uid":22974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T12:56:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1d74fc1bfa309d4e3def12740f8e53173463348b","tid":569191,"uid":47052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1b69a5d04f9eb7d956e6f0d1bf2c82d2f5a7b561","tid":569191,"uid":22974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T12:56:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T13:43:56.000Z","msg":"巴打，樣衰唔緊要，努力工作賺錢，識氹下女仔唔驚冇埋身，你睇八両金都有老婆啦"},{"pid":"146586a65bac3ac34d72fd0470e71d522482643d","tid":569191,"uid":141200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T13:45:46.000Z","msg":"有邊個唔係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}